</p><p class="- topic/p ">The test can be used to fill ink tubes after servicing or to check the ink pumps. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See 
<xref keyref="02ADJU001" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-4A9855DA-F3E3-4188-88E5-42BD74907F2D.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>02 How to refill the ink system</xref> for the correct procedure. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-92369981-F020-4E62-9707-58F93D054214" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure</title><note id="GUID-6CEF36BF-F285-4778-BEEE-1023A059D879" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">DO NOT EXECUTE THIS TEST WITH THE INK TUBES CONNECTED TO THE PRINTHEADS! 
</p></note><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The ink in the ink tanks is stirred first. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press Continue. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select a single pump or all pumps to run. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press Continue. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Enter how long to run the pump(s) in seconds. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Value must be between 1 and 7200 seconds. The default is 400 seconds. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press Continue. 
</p></li></ol></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-E4C54F6E-7FBD-467E-A9DF-8C20AA8FEAEE.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>SDS</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
